author: Minecraft
description:
Minecraft is built not just by our developers, but also by our amazing community – and we wouldn’t be here without you! Join Jens Bergensten, Agnes Larsson, and Aether-modder Brandon Pierce as they explain the importance of collaborating with our players (not with the Narrator) who keep pushing Minecraft forward – never stop doing what you’re doing! 

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/
